Nile Virus [16–19]. The incidence and spread of dengue, Ebola, and scrapie have
also been assessed by FORMULA [20–22]. Tropical issues such as the risks of
indoor airborne infection, bioterrorism, and computer viruses also depend on
this important parameter [23–26].

